{"tid":1005537,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【迎豬年】「蹇叔哭師」下下籤預測孟晚舟的未來","createTime":"2019-02-02T09:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T13:50:54.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"05431d48df575822f43803699908c5f37f7f9376","tid":1005537,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:49:01.000Z","msg":"近日中國科技產業龍頭華為的太子女孟晚舟被拘留一事成為國際焦點，日前中國副總理劉鶴剛抵達華盛頓，還未開展任何活動，美國11名高官便跨部門列陣出席記者會，極罕有地高調力數華為23宗控罪，痛斥華為厚顏無恥，並正式提出引渡華為副董事長兼太子女孟晚舟到美國受審。就孟晚舟的來年運勢，《蘋果》求得第五十八號籤「蹇叔哭師」的下下籤，佛隱看到此籤號暗叫「大鑊」，他解釋這是黃大仙靈籤裏，下下籤之中最差。<br />\n<br />\n他指該籤詩引春秋時期「蹇叔哭師」的典故，他指當時秦穆公要出兵攻佔鄭國與晉國等鄰國，忠臣蹇叔極力勸諫，但秦穆公不聽諫言出兵攻打鄭國及晉國大敗，導致三名大元帥兵敗被擒，最後秦兵「倒戈棄甲」獲釋回國，但士氣受損，佛隱以此推測，指孟「怕會周身蟻，可能仲有牢獄之災」。一旦孟的後台保她不住，孟就凶多吉少了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190202/59209542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190202%2F59209542&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2c%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=7763679a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190202%2F59209542&h=f9f29a52\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190202/59209542</a>"},{"pid":"1b42e6223012e231c1c314d7f44d59c90b1c310a","tid":1005537,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T10:34:39.000Z","msg":"最後秦兵「倒戈棄甲」獲釋回國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162f6562e97135dd9134f4942fd0685364ed9861","tid":1005537,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b42e6223012e231c1c314d7f44d59c90b1c310a","tid":1005537,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T10:34:39.000Z","msg":"最後秦兵「倒戈棄甲」獲釋回國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:05:37.000Z","msg":"求美帝自己倒戈唔回國得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65864ddda9c7c3c9f3792287969882e5c2a5e025","tid":1005537,"uid":204803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}